of morons.

548
00:35:12,236 --> 00:35:15,490
So me and Groot will go
with the pirate angel here.

549
00:35:15,656 --> 00:35:16,824
And the morons
will go to Knowhere

550
00:35:16,908 --> 00:35:18,493
to try to stop Thanos.

551
00:35:18,659 --> 00:35:20,578
