- So cool.

552
00:35:20,745 --> 00:35:22,038
For the record...

553
00:35:22,789 --> 00:35:24,123
I know that
you're going with him

554
00:35:24,207 --> 00:35:25,291
because it's where
Thanos isn't.

555
00:35:25,458 --> 00:35:26,959
You know, you really shouldn't

556
