Come on. Come on.

607
00:39:58,189 --> 00:39:59,982
Come on, you gotta get up.

608
00:40:00,149 --> 00:40:02,359
You gotta get up.
Come on. Hey.

609
00:40:03,444 --> 00:40:04,862
Hey. We have to go.

610
