Gamora.

637
00:43:24,311 --> 00:43:25,312
Come.

638
00:43:25,688 --> 00:43:26,689
Let me help you.

639
00:43:40,202 --> 00:43:41,328
Look.

640
00:43:44,999 --> 00:43:46,667
