leads to Thanos.

658
00:44:50,439 --> 00:44:51,940
Which is what
the grenades are for.

659
00:44:52,858 --> 00:44:55,194
Uh, I'm sorry.
What's the favor?

660
00:44:57,529 --> 00:44:58,530
If things go wrong...

661
00:45:00,115 --> 00:45:02,284
If Thanos gets me...

662
00:45:06,830 --> 00:45:08,791
I want you to promise me...

663
00:45:09,833 --> 00:45:10,959
